message.body: Wow, it's freezing today...
Hahaha. And still not asleep then I see.
I heard that it was from ya news! I could feel it earlier downstairs. The temperature plummeted! Time to Bundle up! And listen to Wd Sheeran ;)
*thep
Hahah nope. You're up earlier today? Or did you randomly wake up in the midst of sleep?
Nah, I'm heading to Dunkin right now.
Oh gotcha. Almost done with the operational changes?
Today should be the last day
Oh good. Get to sleep in some more after this?
Lol yes. I've been so tired.
:( at least you're almost done. Down that coffee!
Or tea, whatever your preference hahah :)
Eh, haven't had much coffee in a while
Me either. I'm afraid I'm going to start shaking if I start drinking it again.
I've heard of people having that issue... I think that means you don't drink it enough.
Yea, might be a kind of shock to the system.
Oh and happy Friday!
Happy Friday! Any plans for today?
Baking for Valentine's! Are you excited for dinner?
Eh. Haven't really thought about it. What cha baking?
I'm thinking about chocolate chip cookies, cupcakes, and might be making candy. It's not all for me by the ways hahah! Getting together at Brenda's for V-Day.
Lol nice! Sounds like fun. Say hi to Brenda for me.
Sure thing!
Steve it's cold!!!
And I'm sitting inside under a blanket!
